snippet.title: Spectral Scream | Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Game Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2620240/Spectral_Scream/

"Spectral Scream", a horror party game is an online co-op horror game for 1-4 players. 

Players, lured by a mysterious flyer promising easy money and driven by greed and desire, 
soon find themselves embarking on a perilous adventure to retrieve the core of Purgatory, 
risking their very lives.

📌Join our channel list
